1 A BILL for an Act to amend and reenact section 57-15-41 of the North Dakota Century Code,
2 relating to the exemption of infrastructure fees from levy limitations.
3 BE IT ENACTED BY THE LEGISLATIVE ASSEMBLY OF NORTH DAKOTA:
4 SECTION 1. AMENDMENT. Section 57-15-41 of the North Dakota Century Code is
5 amended and reenacted as follows:
6 57-15-41. Political subdivision tax levies for payment of special assessments exempt
7 from levy limitations.
8 No taxTax levy limitations provided by any statute of this state may not apply to tax levies by
9 any county, city, school district, park district, or township for the purpose of paying any special
10 assessments and any infrastructure fee provided in sections 11 - 09.1 - 05, 11 - 11 - 55.1 ,
11 40 - 05.1 - 06, and 40 - 22 - 01.3 or paying debt service on bonds issued to prepay special
12 assessments made in accordance with the provisions of title 40, against property owned by
13 such county, city, school district, park district, or township. Any surplus in the special
14 assessment fund after all of the special assessments for which the fund was created have been
15 paid shall be placed in the general fund of the political subdivision.
